com.github.dandelion.core.storage.support

Class BundleDag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dandelion.core.storage.support.BundleDag

  • public class BundleDag
extends Object

    Implementation of a directed acyclic graph adapted to Dandelion.

    In this graph, all verticies are BundleStorageUnit.

    Part of this code has been kindly borrowed and adapted from Michal Maczka, who contributed a DAG implementation to Plexus Utils.

    Since:
    0.10.0
    Author:
    Thibault Duchateau
